text: Jan Skoczylas (born 24 September 1951) is a Polish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:People from Olesno County
